  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Immerse yourself in the heartwarming world of Emotional Art Hidden Objects Game.</h2>\"Love is...\" is an emotional art hidden objects game created with hand-drawn illustrations by the global star artist 'Puuung.' Experience the beauty of watercolor spreading and filling the artwork as you find hidden objects. Discover new hidden objects along with heartwarming stories.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034130/extras/37ed6c8c957a30e26f324757b0583322.poster.avif?t=1724734627\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034130/extras/37ed6c8c957a30e26f324757b0583322.webm?t=1724734627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034130/extras/37ed6c8c957a30e26f324757b0583322.mp4?t=1724734627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Find hidden objects to fully color and complete beautiful paintings.</h2>As you find hidden objects, colors will spread, beautifully filling the artwork. Complete over 280 heartfelt hand-drawn watercolor illustrations. The unique coloring engine of \"Love is...\" offers you an emotional and intense experience.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034130/extras/3e628ed67042c2b80659be2438a0aa77.poster.avif?t=1724734627\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034130/extras/3e628ed67042c2b80659be2438a0aa77.webm?t=1724734627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034130/extras/3e628ed67042c2b80659be2438a0aa77.mp4?t=1724734627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Immerse Yourself In A Warm and Lovely story.</h2>Dive into a heartwarming animation with a sometimes serene, sometimes comic love story. Over an hour of high-quality story animation is prepared for you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034130/extras/95c51ddeb512a1791e49aeb908624ce7.poster.avif?t=1724734627\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034130/extras/95c51ddeb512a1791e49aeb908624ce7.webm?t=1724734627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034130/extras/95c51ddeb512a1791e49aeb908624ce7.mp4?t=1724734627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Keep Beautiful Wallpapers.</h2>With each chapter you clear in \"Love is...\", you will receive beautiful wallpapers. Keep 34 stunning high-quality wallpapers on your PC forever.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034130/extras/4388da83d29f82d08ecb7bbcb5ecf9e2.poster.avif?t=1724734627\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034130/extras/4388da83d29f82d08ecb7bbcb5ecf9e2.webm?t=1724734627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034130/extras/4388da83d29f82d08ecb7bbcb5ecf9e2.mp4?t=1724734627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enjoy the Sweet Ost Of \"Love Is...\"</h2>Enjoy the unplugged OST with its sweet melodies of piano and acoustic guitar.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034130/extras/d6986cfb6583c5d836e7dd4af681f054.poster.avif?t=1724734627\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034130/extras/d6986cfb6583c5d836e7dd4af681f054.webm?t=1724734627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034130/extras/d6986cfb6583c5d836e7dd4af681f054.mp4?t=1724734627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
